parse.title: Bilbo Baggins Global Cafe and Restaurant

wikitext.*:
'''Bilbo Baggins Global Wine Cafe and Restaurant''' was a restaurant situated in Alexandria, Virginia which was themed around none other than [[Bilbo Baggins]] and [[Hobbits]]. It was opened in [[1980]] by Michael Armellino and closed permanently in [[2020]].<ref name="living">{{Cite web|articleurl=https://alexandrialivingmagazine.com/food-and-dining/bilbo-baggins-restaurant-bar-alexandria-va-closes/|articlename=After 40 Years, Bilbo Baggins Closes Its Doors|author=Mary Ann Barton|website=[https://alexandrialivingmagazine.com Alexandria Living Magazine]|dated=29 December 2020}}</ref><ref name="connection">{{Cite web|articleurl=https://www.connectionnewspapers.com/news/2006/may/10/one-cafe-to-rule-them-all/|articlename=One Caf√© to Rule Them All|website=[https://www.connectionnewspapers.com The Connection]|dated=10 May 2006}}</ref>
